@@eThe World of Ack!@@N

In the beginning, the world was forged from chaos and order, twin forces
that shaped the land, the seas, and the skies. The ancient builders
raised great cities and carved deep dungeons into the bones of the earth.

Over countless ages, kingdoms rose and fell, leaving behind ruins filled
with treasure and danger. The world today is a tapestry of civilizations,
wild frontiers, and forgotten places waiting to be rediscovered.

Adventurers come from all corners of the realm, drawn by the promise of
glory, gold, and the thrill of the unknown.

